hopobject.body: magic story very thanks medora.com Married life hasn't been so fair for Christopher Knight and Adrianne Curry. On the five-year anniversary of their wedding, the 'My Fair Brady' stars have decided to call it quits. Knight, 53, best known for his role as Peter Brady on the '70s hit 'The Brady Bunch,' first met Curry, 28, the winner of the first season of 'America's Next Top Model,' in 2004 when they were housemates on the fourth season of VH1's 'The Surreal Life.' Their reality TV romance led to their own VH1 spinoff series, which followed the couple's engagement, wedding and first year of marriage.
